    "cnWords": "我叫Leonard Ross。Brennan先生，我不认识什么Russo，也不认识什么Vinnie。您搞错人了。",
    "enWords": "My name is Leonard Ross. Mr. Brennan, I don't know any Russo, and I don't know any Vinnie. You have the wrong man.",
