    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "我们向Vinnie出示了你的照片。他脱口而出的不是Ross——而是Russo。他一看到你的脸，第一反应叫的是你的真名。",
    "enWords": "We showed Vinnie your photograph. The name that came out of his mouth wasn't Ross — it was Russo. The moment he saw your face, his first instinct was your real name.",
