    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "而且Moore银行的入职档案白纸黑字——1915年前后，Leonard Russo正式改名为Leonard Ross。一个陌生人为什么会叫出你改掉十年的旧姓？",
    "enWords": "And Moore Bank's employment records confirm it in black and white — around 1915, Leonard Russo officially changed his name to Leonard Ross. Why would a stranger call you by a surname you discarded a decade ago?",
    "next": "220005",
