    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "很多移民都改过名字，Brennan先生。在这个国家，意大利姓氏不会为你打开任何一扇门。这证明不了什么。",
    "enWords": "A lot of immigrants changed their names, Mr. Brennan. An Italian surname doesn't open doors in this country. That proves nothing.",
