    "IdSpeaker": "NPC201",
    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "改名不是问题，Leonard。问题是你说你不认识Vinnie——可一个你'不认识'的人，怎么会脱口叫出你十年前改掉的旧姓？你们不是萍水相逢，是旧识。",
    "enWords": "Changing your name isn't the issue, Leonard. The issue is you said you don't know Vinnie — yet a man you 'don't know' blurted out a surname you discarded a decade ago. You two aren't strangers. You go way back.",
    "next": "220007",
