    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "好吧。我承认我以前叫Russo。Vinnie和我小时候在同一条街上长大。但那是二十年前的事了——我走了正道，进了银行。Vinnie走了他的路。我们之间现在没有任何往来，更没有什么金钱关系。",
    "enWords": "Fine. I admit I used to be Russo. Vinnie and I grew up on the same street. But that was twenty years ago — I went straight, joined the bank. Vinnie went his own way. We have no contact now, and certainly no financial connection.",
    "next": "220008",
