    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "没有。我是银行的贷款专员，每天经手的钱比你一年挣的都多——但每一分都走正规流程。和Vinnie？不存在金钱往来。",
    "enWords": "None. I'm a bank loan officer. More money passes through my hands in a day than you earn in a year — but every cent goes through proper channels. With Vinnie? No financial dealings whatsoever.",
