    "cnWords": "O'Hara太太还贷时收到的钞票——全是崭新的二十美元面额，序列号从A73625900B到914B。连号新钞，只有银行才拿得出来。",
    "enWords": "The bills Mrs. O'Hara received for her loan repayment — brand-new twenties, serial numbers A73625900B through 914B. Consecutive new bills. Only a bank issues those.",
