    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "但905到908四张不见了。巧的是，Vinnie在赌场花掉的钞票——序列号恰好是A73625905B到908B。同一批钞票，同一天从银行取出，中间缺失的部分完美吻合。",
    "enWords": "But four bills are missing — 905 through 908. And wouldn't you know it, the bills Vinnie spent at the gambling hall have serial numbers A73625905B through 908B. Same batch, withdrawn the same day, and the missing portion fits perfectly.",
