    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "不是相近，Leonard。是连号。900到904在O'Hara手里，905到908在Vinnie手里。同一次取款，被分成了两份——一份去催债，一份抽走当佣金。钱从银行出来，经你的手，流到了Vinnie口袋里。",
    "enWords": "Not similar — sequential. 900 through 904 in O'Hara's hands, 905 through 908 in Vinnie's. One withdrawal, split in two — one portion for the collection, the other skimmed as commission. The money left the bank, passed through your hands, and ended up in Vinnie's pocket.",
