    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "你在编故事，Brennan先生。序列号只能证明钞票来自同一家银行。几百个客户每天从我们银行取钱——你怎么证明是我经手的？",
    "enWords": "You're weaving a story, Mr. Brennan. Serial numbers only prove the bills came from the same bank. Hundreds of clients withdraw money from us every day — how do you prove it passed through my hands?",
