    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "而且还有这个——Vinnie的催债小本子。日期、地址、上门记录，一笔一笔写得清清楚楚。末尾还有一条备注：'Russo给的地址有问题，下次问清楚'。Russo——Leonard Ross的旧姓。这不是借钱跑腿，这是系统性的雇佣催收。",
    "enWords": "And then there's this — Vinnie's collection book. Dates, addresses, visit logs, all written down in detail. And at the bottom, a note: 'Russo gave me the wrong address, need to ask next time.' Russo — Leonard Ross's old name. This isn't casual errand-running. This is systematic, hired debt collection.",
    "next": "220025",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
    "ParameterStr2": "",
