    "cnLocation": "审讯室",
    "enLocation": "Interrogation Room"
  },
  {
    "id": 220025,
    "step": 25,
    "speakType": 2,
    "waitTime": 0,
    "IdSpeaker": "NPC204",
    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "...你不了解南区是怎么运作的，Brennan先生。那些人——他们借了钱就不还。催款函寄出去像石沉大海。银行需要有人去敲他们的门。",
    "enWords": "...You don't understand how the South Side works, Mr. Brennan. Those people — they borrow and never pay back. Collection notices disappear like stones in a lake. The bank needs someone to knock on their doors.",
    "next": "220026",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
    "ParameterStr2": "",
    "ParameterInt0": 0,
    "ParameterInt1": 0,
