  },
  {
    "id": 220026,
    "step": 26,
    "speakType": 2,
    "waitTime": 0,
    "IdSpeaker": "NPC201",
    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "敲门？Vinnie在O'Hara家门口留了威胁便条——'再不还钱，下次就不只是警告。'他闯进我母亲的鞋坊，把一个老太太吓得不敢开门。你管这叫敲门？",
    "enWords": "Knocking? Vinnie left a threatening note at the O'Haras' door — 'Pay up or next time it won't just be a warning.' He barged into my mother's shoe shop and terrified an old woman into locking her door. You call that knocking?",
    "next": "220027",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
    "ParameterStr2": "",
    "ParameterInt0": 0,
