    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "...我只是告诉Vinnie去催收。他怎么做的，那不是我能控制的。",
    "enWords": "...I only told Vinnie to collect. How he went about it — that's beyond my control.",
    "next": "220028",
