    "step": 28,
    "speakType": 2,
    "waitTime": 0,
    "IdSpeaker": "NPC201",
    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "你雇了一个有暴力前科的人去恐吓欠款的穷人，然后从中抽佣。你知道他会做什么——你就是需要他做那些事。",
    "enWords": "You hired a man with a violent record to intimidate debtors, and you took a cut. You knew what he would do — that's precisely why you needed him.",
    "next": "220029",
