    "IdSpeaker": "NPC204",
    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "好了，我承认我雇了Vinnie催收。但这在整个行业里都是公开的秘密——每家银行都这么干。你以为你能拿这个扳倒我？",
    "enWords": "Enough. I admit I hired Vinnie for collections. But it's an open secret across the entire industry — every bank does it. You think you can take me down with this?",
    "next": "220030",
