    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "你没有搜查令，没有传票。银行的内部记录，你连碰都碰不到。想要查Moore银行的账目？先去找法官签字吧。",
    "enWords": "You have no search warrant, no subpoena. You can't even touch the bank's internal records. Want to look at Moore Bank's ledgers? Go get a judge to sign off first.",
