    "IdSpeaker": "NPC201",
    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "我会拿到那些记录的，Leonard。连号钞票、Vinnie的口供、催债日志——这些已经够让任何一个法官签搜查令了。",
    "enWords": "I'll get those records, Leonard. Consecutive serial numbers, Vinnie's testimony, the collection log — that's more than enough for any judge to sign a warrant.",
